      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="37517663">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/34019008/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u34019008-23.jpg" alt="Winter" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37517663/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37517663/" class="">第22页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/34019008/" class=" " title="Winter">Winter</a>
                (可是我，真的一无所有)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37517663">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">在货币交易范围内人人在价值上平等，不是因为每个人都有价值，而是因为除了金钱没有人有价值。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-04-05 16:15</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>在货币交易范围内人人在价值上平等，不是因为每个人都有价值，而是因为除了金钱没有人有价值。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







